Deeꞌ naa lah raꞌ bwiinn raꞌ nin guhca raꞌ xtulbaaꞌ Jesucristu, lliiꞌn Davihd, lliiꞌn Abrahn.
Ya chin bihn rrehyi Herodes nin guhdzi raꞌ rrehyi mago raꞌ chi dxyihgah si guhca ziahan loh xigaaba ba; ziꞌchi gahca za guzahca raꞌ garaa raꞌ bwiinn guihdxyi Jerusalehn.
Laꞌh Jwahn ruzeꞌta profeta Isaías chin bacaꞌh ba squiiꞌ:
―Neezaa caa loh Xchihtsi Dxiohs: “Ayi guunn tu pwexta laꞌh Dxiohs nin rnabwaꞌ.”
’Dichohsa raꞌ bwiinn nin cachiaꞌhan cun nin cadxahga ñihsa, laasii pur nin saꞌloh guunn raꞌ ba nin xclaaꞌdzi Dxiohs guunn raꞌ ba, pwihsi laꞌh gahca Ñiꞌh zahcanee Ñiꞌh laꞌh raꞌ ba tin guzaꞌloh raꞌ ba ziga xclaaꞌdzi Ñiꞌh guunn raꞌ ba.
Per naꞌh rñiꞌn loh tu, sidela laꞌh tuhbi ndxiꞌhw taaꞌha ba cheꞌhla ba nicala ayi naa gunnaꞌh chiꞌh bwiinn gubwihlli, ndxiꞌhw chi zuhnn dxiaaba gunnaꞌh chi loh guelgubwihlli chuu xtuꞌh bi, ya nin guchinaa cun tuhbi gunnaꞌh gubwihlli, naa za ba tuhbi bwiinn gubwihlli.
Laꞌh tu nahpa cwidxyi tu Dxiohs squiiꞌ:
Rahbi za Ñiꞌh:
ya biaaba tuhbi ñihsadxiah xihn ya biehta ñisyuhdoꞌ guiꞌw raꞌ cun bwih duxa ya bacwihin yuuꞌ chi nin rraxtra yuuꞌ chi ayi biaꞌhan.
Ya chin bwaꞌha Jesuhs ziahan raꞌ bwiinn rii gadiidxi Ñiꞌh, chiꞌchi gunabwaꞌ Ñiꞌh tiidxinee Ñiꞌh xpwiinn raꞌ Ñiꞌh stuhbi lahdu rwaaꞌ laguhn,
ya riꞌchi gwanee raꞌ bwiinn tuhbi bwiinn nin ayi guhca ñiñiꞌbi, naꞌ ba loh tuhbi luꞌhn, ya chin bwaꞌha Jesuhs ziga riachiistoꞌ raꞌ bwiinn chi laꞌh Ñiꞌh, chiꞌchi rahbi Ñiꞌh loh bwiinn nin rahcalluꞌhu chi:
ya loh zeezah Jesuhs guyuuꞌ tuhbi gunnaꞌh nin zeenaꞌhla laꞌh Ñiꞌh; gunnaꞌh riiꞌ naa la tsiꞌh bichiohpa yihza canee bi tuhbi gueldxyihdxyi xteenn nin naa bi gunnaꞌh ya hohra chi gwabiiga bi nez dihtsi Jesuhs ya bidxiꞌ bi loh xahba Ñiꞌh,
ya chiꞌchi rahbi Ñiꞌh loh raꞌ xpwiinn Ñiꞌh:
Rahbi za Jesuhs:
Ya sidela ayi niꞌchi dxiꞌh, ¿xiilla gwaguiaꞌha si chiꞌh tu? ¿Ta gwaguiaꞌha tu tuhbi ndxiꞌhw nin nahcu lahdxi zaꞌca? Laꞌh tu naann tu sola yihdzi tuhbi bwiinn nin rnabwaꞌ duxa nuu bwiinn raꞌ nin nahcu lahdxi zaꞌca.
Pwihsi guyuuꞌtii ba laꞌn xquidoꞌ Dxiohs tin gudahw ba pahn nin ayi nuu gahw raꞌ bwiinn ziga xpwiinn ba o ziga laꞌh za ba, laasii laꞌh dxiꞌh raꞌ bixohza rahca rahw pahn chi.
Ya ziꞌchi gahca za sidela laꞌh bwiinndxaaba rabweꞌhe gahca ba laꞌh nin naa za bwiinndxaaba stoꞌ raꞌ bwiinn pwihsi zilaaꞌha lasaaꞌ raꞌ ba, ya pwihsi ¿xaalla cheezah chuu xquelrnabwaꞌ raꞌ ba?
―Bwiinn raꞌ riiꞌ naa xmaaꞌn cun bwihtsi raꞌn,
per ya laasii ayi nahpa raꞌ ba ziga dulbaaꞌ chaꞌyi, niꞌchin nin ayi riazahnee raꞌ ba xchiꞌdxyi Dxiohs cun gaduhbi xigaaba raꞌ ba, ya balaaquiꞌhn si rzaꞌcazii raꞌ ba o rdxyiꞌchinee raꞌ bwiinn laꞌh raꞌ ba pur xcweenta xchiꞌdxyi Dxiohs niꞌchin rbweꞌhe stoꞌ raꞌ ba xchiꞌdxyi Dxiohs.
―Guelrnabwaꞌ xteenn Dxiohs naa ziga tuhbi cohsa zaꞌca duxa nin nuulaꞌn taayi loh yuh, ya tuhbi ndxiꞌhw rdxeela cohsa zaꞌca duxa chi, ya loh rdxeela ban rusieꞌwgahca ba yihcan ya riahxi duxa ba rbiaꞌgarii ba tin riagatooꞌ ba garaa nin nahpa ba tin rziꞌ ba loh yuh hasta bidxeela ba cohsa zaꞌca chi.
per dxyihyi nin guhca dxyihlah Herodes, chiꞌchi badxiaꞌha lliiꞌndxaꞌpa Herodías pur nin guhca dxyihlah Herodes galaayi loh raꞌ ba, ya pur nin badxiaꞌha dxaꞌpa chi biahxi duxa Herodes,
―Daada, sidela yiꞌhin, gunabwaꞌ dxieꞌldahn hasta zuu Yuꞌbiluꞌh nee saꞌhn loh ñihsa.
Chiꞌchi rahbi Jesuhs loh raꞌ ba:
Chiꞌchi gudihdxyi Jesuhs xpwiinn Ñiꞌh tin rahbi Ñiꞌh loh raꞌ ba:
―¿Chyu niꞌca rahbi raꞌ bwiinn naahn?
Ya chin bihn raꞌ gadxiohnna xpwiinn Ñiꞌh dxyiꞌdxyi raꞌ chi hasta loh yuh guhta gurloh raꞌ ba laasii bidxyihbi duxa raꞌ ba,
Ya loh zeeyuuꞌtii Pehdru rwaaꞌ yuuꞌ mwergaloh guñiꞌ Jesuhs rahbi Ñiꞌh loh ba:
’Pwihsi guchiin nin rñiꞌn loh tu garaa raꞌ xtuhlda bwiinn nin gusiaꞌlda stoꞌ tu loh guidxyiyuh riiꞌ, garaa za niꞌchi raꞌ zusiaꞌlda stoꞌ Dxiohs xcweenta raꞌ ba, ya duhlda raꞌ nin ayi dxiaꞌldastoꞌ tu loh guidxyiyuh riiꞌ ayi za chapitii raꞌn nez llaaꞌndxibaaꞌ loh Dxiohs.
―¿Xixnaa chiꞌh basiaꞌhannee guehtu Moisehs dxihtsi laꞌh nu: “Cun gudiꞌhi ndxiꞌhw tuhbi dxihtsi laꞌh xcunnaꞌh ba, bachiꞌh ziꞌchi ba guruuꞌn lasaaꞌ raꞌ ba”?
Ya chin bihn raꞌ xpwiinn Ñiꞌh dxyiꞌdxyi raꞌ nin guñiꞌ Ñiꞌh, badxyigaaꞌ duxa raꞌ ba pur dxyiꞌdxyi raꞌ chi, ya chiꞌchi rahbi raꞌ ba:
chiꞌchi rahbi Jesuhs loh xnaan raꞌ bi:
―Gulcheh loh rrandxu nin naa gahxu neziiꞌ, riꞌchi zwaꞌha tu caduꞌh tuhbi buhrra cun lliiꞌn ma. Ya gulgaxachi ma tin dxieꞌnee tu ma,
―Guchiin nin rñiꞌn loh tu sidela laꞌh tu riachiistoꞌ tu xchiꞌdxyi Dxiohs nee ayi guunn chiohpa stoꞌ tu, ayi nin bwiꞌhnn si dxiꞌhn cun yahga ñiigu riiꞌ gaca guunn tu sino que neezaa loh tuhbi dahan gahbi tu: “Biyaꞌdxu riꞌca tin balaꞌha yiꞌh loh ñihsadoꞌ”, zahca gacan,
Yannah chin dxieꞌguiaꞌha ballwaaꞌn xteenn loh yuh chi, ¿xiniꞌca gunnee ba laꞌh raꞌ bwiinn nin guuꞌn loh xuh ba garoolda?
―Bwiinn dxixiꞌhw raꞌ, ¿xixnaa xclaaꞌdzi tu guunn tu prehba naꞌh?
Pwihsi garoopa dxyiꞌdxyi riiꞌ xteenn xlehyi Moisehs naa ziga dulbaaꞌ loh raꞌ snuhn raꞌ dxyiꞌdxyi lehyi, ziga xlehyi guehtu Moisehs o ziga xlehyi raꞌ guehtu daada raꞌ nin guñiꞌ xchiꞌdxyi Dxiohs cadxyih.
¡Bwiinn nahda raꞌ bwiinn dxieꞌpa raꞌ! ¿Cuun nin lasahca ru? ¿Ta ohro o guidoꞌ nin ruhnntaaꞌyi yihca ohro?
―Gulgahca nasiin tin ayi gusaaꞌn tu gusaguiꞌhi raꞌ bwiinn laꞌh tu,
pwihsi ziꞌchi gahca za chin gwaꞌha tu laꞌh garaa raꞌ deeꞌ cayahca, laꞌh gahca tu gacabwaꞌ tu laꞌh dxyih zeꞌgadzihn gahxu gabiaꞌgarii Lliiꞌn Dxiohs; hasta rwaaꞌ leeꞌ zeꞌgadzihn Ñiꞌh.
Ya gaduhbi nin zee siꞌ raꞌ dxaꞌpa raꞌ nin ayi guinasiin raꞌ chi xnsehchi raꞌ bi, bieꞌ nin bachinaa, ya laꞌh raꞌ dxaꞌpa raꞌ nin nasiin raꞌ chi biuꞌgariinee raꞌ bi laꞌh nin bachinaa chi laꞌn yuuꞌ ya riinee raꞌ bi laꞌh nin bachinaa chi hasta cayahca saaꞌ, ya cun bieꞌw rwaaꞌ yuuꞌ chi,
Ya garaa raꞌ nin bwiꞌhnn raꞌ gahn loh guelrnabwaꞌ xteenn Dxiohs ziñiꞌ raꞌ ba squiiꞌ: “Daada Dxiohs, ¿cuuca lla bidiaꞌha nu yiꞌh zuuchiaꞌhan luꞌh nee baniꞌhi nu guelwahw gudahw luꞌh?, nee ¿cuuca za bidiaꞌha nu yiꞌh rdxahga luꞌh ñihsa nee baniꞌhi za nu ñihsa gwaaꞌ luꞌh?,
ya hohra chi gahca cadxiꞌhyi ba xa guunn ba gutiꞌdxi ba laꞌh Jesuhs loh raꞌ bwiinn chi.
Chiꞌchi rahbi Jesuhs:
Ya chiꞌchi gwabiiga raꞌ bwiinn nin zeꞌnee Judas tin gunaꞌzu raꞌ ba laꞌh Jesuhs,
Ya gaduhbi nin zohba Pehdru laaꞌyitiaaꞌha xteenn rwaaꞌ yihdzi bixohza nin rnabwaꞌ chi, chiꞌchi badzihn tuhbi gunnaꞌh nin ruhnn dziꞌn riꞌchi ziga mooza, ya gwabiiga bi hasta zohba Pehdru chiꞌchi rahbi bi loh ba:
―Yiꞌh gahca guñiꞌ luꞌhn.
per galoh Pilahtu gwanee raꞌ ba laꞌh Jesuhs hasta naa palasiu ya riꞌchi badiaaꞌha raꞌ ba garaa raꞌ ba gadiidxi Ñiꞌh.
ya baꞌ raꞌ billaala raꞌn, ya ziahan raꞌ nin naa raꞌ xpwiinn Dxiohs babahn raꞌ ba loh guelguhchi hohra chi,
Ya gaduhbi ziaa raꞌ gunnaꞌh raꞌ chi, gubiaꞌgarii raꞌ za paaldaa suldahdu raꞌ loh guihdxyi Jerusalehn tin gwaguihtsi raꞌ ba loh raꞌ bixohza raꞌ nin rnabwaꞌ laꞌh raꞌ bixohza garaa raꞌ nin bwaꞌha raꞌ ba guhca rwaaꞌ baꞌ.
Ya seguihdu gahca gwanee Spíritu Saantu laꞌh Jesuhs loh tuhbi dahan desiertu,
―Ziahan raꞌ bwiinn xclaaꞌdzi gwaꞌha yiꞌh.
―Gudaaꞌnaꞌhla naꞌh.
chiꞌchi bwaꞌha nadxyiꞌchi Jesuhs loh raꞌ garaa raꞌ bwiinn nin rii gadiidxi Ñiꞌh ya guhca nalaasa stoꞌ Ñiꞌh laasii bwaꞌha Ñiꞌh ayi riaa lasaaꞌ raꞌ ba, chiꞌchi rahbi Ñiꞌh loh ndxiꞌhw nin gubihdzi naa ñiꞌh chi:
31-32 Ya xmah Jesuhs cun bwihtsi raꞌ Ñiꞌh badzihn raꞌ ba hasta cagaluuꞌyi Ñiꞌh, per ayi guhca ñabiiga raꞌ ba hasta zuu Ñiꞌh laasii dxiꞌbi ziahan raꞌ bwiinn rii riꞌchi, niꞌchin guyuuꞌ nin badiꞌhi rsohn laꞌh raꞌ bwiinn nin zohba gadiidxi cweeꞌ Jesuhs rahbi raꞌ ba loh Ñiꞌh:
Rahbi za Jesuhs loh raꞌ ba:
bariaꞌh Jesuhs laꞌn barcu, lwehgu badxiꞌloh Ñiꞌh laꞌh tuhbi ndxiꞌhw nin nuu bwiinndxaaba stoꞌ ñiꞌh,
Ya loh zeenee Jesuhs laꞌh Jairu, neezaa ziahan duxa raꞌ bwiinn zeenaꞌhla laꞌh raꞌ ba, hasta bateꞌh raꞌ ba laꞌh Ñiꞌh,
―¿Ca nehza basiꞌdxi deeꞌ ziahan dxyiꞌdxyi raꞌ riiꞌ? ¿Ca nehza gwacaꞌha ndxiꞌhw ca lligaaba nasiin cun dziꞌn roo raꞌ nin ruhnn ba?
ya chin guyuuꞌtii lliiꞌndxaꞌpa gahca Herodías laꞌn hasta rii raꞌ Herodes cun garaa raꞌ xpwiinn ba loh mwella, chiꞌchi badxiaꞌha dxaꞌpa chi, ya biuꞌstoꞌ duxa rrehyi Herodes cun garaa raꞌ nin zohbanee ba loh mweella ziga badxiaꞌha dxaꞌpa chi, chiꞌchi rahbi Herodes loh dxaꞌpa chi:
Ya chin bwaꞌha raꞌ ba chiꞌchi rahbi raꞌ ba:
Lliaaꞌh naa zi ruzuꞌnllihbi tu nez loon, laasii laꞌh tu ruluuꞌyi tu nin naa gahca xcostumbre tu nee rahbi tu naa raꞌn nin gunabwaꞌ Dxiohs.
―Bwehngahca guñiꞌ luꞌh, zahca guziaa luꞌh, ya laꞌh bwiinndxaaba chi bariaꞌh stoꞌ lliiꞌndxaꞌpa luꞌh.
Ya cun basaaꞌn Ñiꞌh laꞌh raꞌ ba riꞌchi lwehgu bacah Ñiꞌh laꞌn laancha zeenee chiꞌh Ñiꞌh laꞌh raꞌ xpwiinn Ñiꞌh stuhbi lahdu rwaaꞌ ñihsa.
―Yiꞌh nin naa luꞌh Crixtu Lliiꞌn Dxiohs nin dxuleꞌza nu.
per rñiꞌn loh tu laꞌh Elías biꞌ la ya laꞌh raꞌ bwiinn bwiꞌhnnee raꞌ ba laꞌh ba zigachiꞌzi guclaaꞌdzi raꞌ ba ziga rñiꞌ loh Xchihtsi Dxiohs.
―Nahpa zutiꞌdxi raꞌ bwiinn duhlda naꞌh loh raꞌ nin rnabwaꞌ, ya zidxiinn raꞌ ba naꞌh, per chin dxiohnna dxyih guhchiꞌhn, zabahnaꞌhn loh raꞌ bwiinn guuchi.
Chiꞌchi rahbi raꞌ ba loh Ñiꞌh:
Ya badxyigaaꞌ duxa loh raꞌ xpwiinn Ñiꞌh chin bihn raꞌ ba nin guñiꞌ Ñiꞌh, chiꞌchi rahbi Ñiꞌh stuhbi:
chiꞌchi gudihdxyi Jesuhs laꞌh raꞌ ba ya rahbi Ñiꞌh:
ya chin baganee raꞌ ba ma hasta zuu Jesuhs, chiꞌchi badziiꞌba raꞌ ba xahba raꞌ ba dihtsi ma, tin guzohba Jesuhs dihtsi ma,
Guldxixteeꞌ loon: ¿Chyu guxeꞌhla laꞌh Jwahn bieꞌgaroꞌbañihsa ba? ¿Ta Dxiohs guluꞌnehza laꞌh ba o bwiinn zi raꞌ?
―¿Chyu yihca caa lohon, cun chyu laa caa lohon?
―¿Xa mohda rñiꞌ raꞌ mwehsu nin ruluuꞌyi lehyi Crixtu naa lliiꞌn guehtu Davihd?
ya garaa raꞌ bwiinn guidxyiyuh guidxyiꞌchinee raꞌ ba laꞌh tu laasii riachiistoꞌ tu xchiꞌdxyiꞌhn, per bwiinn nin ayi cweꞌhestoꞌ ñiꞌh xchiꞌdxyiꞌhn bwiinn chi taꞌh loh duhlda tin guziaa ba dxibaaꞌ.
ya bidxyiꞌchi nuhn raꞌ nin rii riꞌchi, chiꞌchi rahbi loh lasaaꞌ raꞌ ba:
―Vihnnu riiꞌ naa ziga rihn nin nuuꞌhuhn, nin guilliꞌhihn chin chiinn raꞌ ba naꞌh xcweenta ziahan raꞌ bwiinn guidxyiyuh,
Ya Judas nin biuꞌn ntriehgu laꞌh Ñiꞌh rahbi loh raꞌ bwiinn duhlda chi nin naa tuhbi sehn gaca squiiꞌ:
Ya nuu raꞌ ba bachah xihin raꞌ ba loh Ñiꞌh cun neezaa basieꞌw raꞌ ba loh Ñiꞌh chiꞌchi guyaꞌzi raꞌ ba loh Ñiꞌh, ya rahbi raꞌ ba:
Squiiꞌ guñiꞌ Pilahtu laasii guhcabwaꞌ ba batiꞌdxi bixohza raꞌ nin rnabwaꞌ laꞌh Ñiꞌh loh ba laasii cadxyiꞌchinee raꞌ ba laꞌh Ñiꞌh xixnaa rianaꞌhla ziahan bwiinn laꞌh Ñiꞌh,
Dxiehta ba loh cruhzi ca ziga naa ba Crixtu nin dxuleꞌza nuꞌh, nee ziga naa za ba rrehyi loh raꞌ bwiinn Israel tin guidiaꞌha loh nuꞌh ya ziꞌchi chechiistoꞌ nuꞌh laꞌh ba.
Chiꞌchi bariaꞌtiiꞌ raꞌ gunnaꞌh chi laꞌn baꞌ cun rdxyihbi duxa raꞌ ba, ayi xi guhdzi raꞌ ba loh nin tuhbi bwiinn.
tin badoꞌ chi gaca bi tuhbi bwiinn nin lasahca duxa loh Dxiohs. Ayi guee bi vihnnu nee nin tuhbiza clahsa ñihsa nin rusuhdzi laꞌh bwiinn, ya zibweeza Spíritu Saantu xteenn Dxiohs lastoꞌ bi dez chin nuu gahca bi stoꞌ xmah bi.
Para Dxiohs garaatiiꞌ rahca; ayi nin tuhbi cohsa nin guunn gahn laꞌh Ñiꞌh.
laasii guziꞌguehlda Dxiohs gacanee Ñiꞌh laꞌh xtatiita Abrahn nuꞌh cun neezaa garaa llahga ba.
tin gacabwaꞌ bwiinn lasaaꞌ raꞌ nuꞌh gusiaꞌpitii Dxiohs xtuhlda raꞌ ba, tin taꞌh raꞌ ba lohon.
Bwiꞌhnn raꞌ ba squiiꞌ laasii ziꞌchi caa loh xlehyi Moisehs: “Garaa lliiꞌn galoh tu nin naa biñiꞌn ndxiꞌhw cwii raꞌ tu bi tin guunn bi xtsiꞌn Dxiohs.”
―Xiiꞌhihn, ¿xixnaa bwiꞌhnnee luꞌh naꞌh ziꞌca? Bwaꞌha, xpah luꞌh neen naꞌh ¡blaaca riacahstoꞌ nu yiꞌh!
Chiꞌchi rahbi Jwahn:
Ya rahbi bwiinndxaaba loh Jesuhs:
Ya garaa raꞌ ba guñiꞌ zaꞌca raꞌ ba pur Jesuhs, cun badxyigaaꞌza raꞌ ba pur dxyiꞌdxyi zaꞌca nin guñiꞌ Jesuhs, ya rahbi loh lasaaꞌ raꞌ ba:
―Nahpa guluuꞌyiꞌhn xchiꞌdxyi xquelrnabwaꞌ Dxiohs ziahan guihdxyi, niꞌchin nin guxeꞌhla Dxiohs naꞌh guidxyiyuh.
―Mihgu, laꞌxtuhlda luꞌh basiaꞌpitiin nnah.
Chiꞌchi rahbi Jesuhs loh raꞌ ba:
’Per prohbi za laꞌh tu rricu raꞌ laasii nnah si gapa tu cohsa zaꞌca.
Xñah ba ziga xñah tuhbi bwiinn nin bazaꞌ tuhbi yuuꞌ. Galoh gudaꞌhn ba gueeta rooꞌ chiꞌchi bwiꞌhnn ba simieentu yihca tuhbi dxiah. Ya chin guyaꞌloh yuuꞌ, chiꞌchi biaaba tuhbi ñihsadxiah xihn, bieꞌta tuhbi ñihsyuhdoꞌ guiꞌw hasta bwiꞌhnn bwiinn chi yuuꞌ. Ya ñihsyuh chi guhcacaaꞌhan tihxi yihdzi ba per nin blaaquiꞌhn ayi bañiꞌbin yuuꞌ chi laasii dziꞌtsi bidxiꞌdxiun yihca dxiah chi.
Ya chin badzihn raꞌ bwiinn chi loh Jesuhs, chiꞌchi rahbi raꞌ ba loh Ñiꞌh:
Chiꞌchi rahbi Jesuhs loh ba:
―Dxiohs gahca rñiꞌ loh tu tin gacabwaꞌ tu cohsa raꞌ xteenn xquelrnabwaꞌ Ñiꞌh. Ya cohsa raꞌ chi ayi guiñiꞌnayaa Ñiꞌhn loh raꞌ bwiinn. Niꞌchin cweenta raꞌ si rñiꞌn loh raꞌ bwiinn tin gwaꞌha raꞌ ba per ayi gacabwaꞌ raꞌ ba; dxihn raꞌ ba per ayi gaann raꞌ ba xiñin.
―¿Xix zeꞌchuu luꞌh riiꞌ, Jesuhs Lliiꞌn Dxiohs nin nuu nabahandziꞌtsi dxibaaꞌ? ¡Rdxiꞌhnaꞌhn loh luꞌh ayi gusaꞌcazii luꞌh naꞌh!
―Nuu tuhbi bwiinn nin bidxiꞌ naꞌh laasii guhcabwaꞌn basiaca xquelrnabwaꞌn laꞌh ba.
Ya chin guhca gudxyih, gwabiiga gadziꞌh bichiohpa xpwiinn Ñiꞌh, ya rahbi raꞌ ba loh Ñiꞌh:
Ya gaduhbi cabwihdxyi-canaaba Ñiꞌh laꞌh Xtaada Dxiohs Ñiꞌh, baluuꞌyiloh guriin xñah Ñiꞌh nee xahba Ñiꞌh biahca labwehen ya gucabachaꞌhan.
―Mwehsu, bidiaꞌha nu loh tuhbi bwiinn nin rabweꞌhe bwiinndxaaba stoꞌ raꞌ bwiinn cun xquelrnabwaꞌ lah luꞌh, ya bachidiꞌtsi nu loh ba ayiru guunn ba ziꞌchi laasii ayi needxiꞌh ba caꞌnzaa ba loh nuꞌh.
Ayi chenee tu manguchi mweeyi, ayiza chenee tu chiohpa nehza xahba tu nin xqueldxihdxyiza tu, nin ayiza guziꞌlaaꞌdzi tu caacazi tin ayi gugahpaDxiohs bwiinn laꞌh tu loh neziuh.
―¿Xa cañiꞌ loh dxihtsi xteenn lehyi, xa ruꞌlda luꞌhn?
―Chin cwidxi-guinaaba tu Dxiohs, squiiꞌ guiñiꞌ tu:
―Chin rariaꞌh bwiinndxaaba stoꞌ tuhbi bwiinn, chiꞌchi rcaꞌnzaa ba lugahri bihdzi tin rdxiꞌhyi ba canehza guziꞌlaaꞌdzi ba, ya rwaꞌhasi ba ayi rdxeelan, ruhnn ba lligaaba: “Mejor gabiaꞌgariin yiidzihn hasta bariaꞌhn.”
’Prohbiza laꞌh tu laasii ruhnnchaꞌyi tu xpaꞌ raꞌ daada raꞌ nin guñiꞌ xchiꞌdxyi Dxiohs cachieempa, nee laꞌh gahca tu nin naa llahga raꞌ bwiinn nin gudxiinn laꞌh raꞌ ba.
―Guyuuꞌ tuhbi bwiinn gohpa ba ziahan cohsa zaꞌca ya guyuuꞌ tuhbi dxyih guhca duxa xquiñaꞌh ba.
Chiꞌchi rahbi Jesuhs:
chiꞌchi rahbi ba loh bwiinn nin rahpa riꞌchi: “Bwaꞌha, guhca chohnna yihza rieꞌldaguiaꞌhan gu nuu xi ñiigu xcah loh yahga riiꞌ, per nin guduhvehsa nagahdxi guidxeelaꞌhn nin tuhbin. Mejor gutaꞌdxuñin, ¿xixgahn cabweꞌhesin xjweersi loh xuun?”
Per nuu raꞌ nin ruhnn lligaaba gulliaaꞌ lasahca raꞌ ba nnah per chiꞌchi zacalasahca duxaru raꞌ ba, nuuza raꞌ nin ruhnn lligaaba lasahca duxa raꞌba nnah ya loh guelrnabwaꞌ chi ayi xi gacalasahcatiiꞌ raꞌ ba.
Chiꞌchi guzaꞌloh guñiꞌ cada tuhbigah raꞌ ba rahbi raꞌ ba ayi nuu chee raꞌ ba, tuhbi ba rahbi: “Gueꞌdu guziꞌn tuhbi taaꞌha loh yuh, nnah nahpa chaguiaꞌhañin rnaꞌbaꞌhn ayi guidxyiꞌchi luꞌh pur ayi saꞌhn”,
Rñaazahn loh tu, ziꞌchi gahcaza riahxinee xaanjla Dxiohs nin rii dxibaaꞌ pur nin rusaguꞌdzistoꞌ tuhbi bwiinn duhlda chezah ba xneziuh Dxiohs.
Chiꞌchi rahbi bwiinn chi: “Nuzaꞌbiꞌhn tuhbi gaywaꞌh barrihyi nsehchi.” Chiꞌchi rahbi mooza chi: “Dee naa xnohta luꞌh yannah guzohba riꞌca tin bwiꞌhnn stuhbin pur chwaꞌhbitsiꞌhsin.”
Rahbi Jesuhs loh raꞌ xpwiinn Ñiꞌh: ―Nahpa nuu cohsa raꞌ nin ruhnn pur riuuꞌ xtuhlda raꞌ bwiinn, per prohbiza bwiinn nin rguꞌtii laꞌh raꞌ bwiinn loh duhlda.
tin par ayi gaca guiñiꞌ tu: “Riiꞌ cayahca niꞌca”, o gahbi tu: “Riꞌchi cayahcan”, laasii dez nnah laꞌDxiohs canabwaꞌla paaldaa bwiinn nin dxaꞌga loh tu.
Rñaan loh tu, lwehgu gahca zuhnn ba guelguxchiisi para laꞌh raꞌ ba. Per chin gabiaꞌgariin, ziga naan Lliiꞌn Dxiohs nin naa ndxiꞌhw guidxyiyuh stuhbi, diaꞌhan ¿gu zidxeelaꞌhn bwiinn nin riachiistoꞌ ñiꞌh xchiꞌdxyiꞌhn?
―Daada, laꞌh nu laꞌnu dxugasaaꞌn garaa nin nadxiahpa nu, tin zioꞌpanaꞌhla nu Yuꞌbiluꞌh.
Lwehgu balluꞌn ba gwah ba delaanta hasta zohba tuhbi llaaꞌn yahga gurooꞌ nin laa sicohmoro nez tiidxi Jesuhs, chiꞌchi gucah ba lohon tin guhca bwaꞌha ba laꞌh Jesuhs.
Ya chin zegadzihn Ñiꞌh tuhbi guihdxyi nin laa Betfageh cun guihdxyi nin laa Betania, gahxu loh dahan nin laa Olivo chiꞌchi guxeꞌhla Ñiꞌh chiohpa xpwiinn Ñiꞌh,
―Gudxixteeꞌ loh nu chyu naa luꞌh tin gaca guunn luꞌh garaa niꞌca o chyu gunnah loh luꞌh guunn luꞌhn.
―Daada, mwehsu; naann nu xnehza rñiꞌ luꞌh nee naannza nu xnehza rusiꞌdxi luꞌh. Ayi rwaꞌhazaꞌca luꞌh loh tuhbi bwiinn ya stuhbigaꞌh ba gwaꞌhadxaaba luꞌh loh ñiꞌh, laasii rusiꞌdxi luꞌh mohdapaꞌ nin ruhnn Dxiohs guelguxchiisi,
Daada Dxiohs rahbi loh Daada nin rnabwaꞌ naꞌh:
Ya chin gwaꞌha bwiinn raꞌ gaca niꞌchi, chiꞌchi nahpa guiriaꞌh raꞌ bwiinn guihdxyi Judea yihdzi raꞌ ba guzee raꞌ ba loh dahan; ya bwiinn nin rii raꞌla loh dahan ayiru guibiaꞌgarii raꞌ ba chegalliꞌhi raꞌ ba xixteenn raꞌ ba yihdzi raꞌ ba,
―¿Canehza xclaaꞌdzi luꞌh gachidiꞌhnnchaꞌyi nu guelwahw?
―Simohn, Simohn; laꞌbwiinndxaaba nin laa Satanahs gunaaba yiꞌh tin tsiibi ba yiꞌh zigazi rbiꞌbi llooba chin nuuꞌhun deh,
―Judas, ¿ta pur tuhbi behsu riiꞌ riuꞌn luꞌh ntriehgu Lliiꞌn Dxiohs nin naa ndxiꞌhw loh raꞌ bwiinn riiꞌ?
Neezaa caguii xaꞌta raꞌ ba loh Ñiꞌh cañiꞌyah duxa raꞌ ba laꞌh Ñiꞌh.
Ya ziahanrooꞌ dxyiꞌdxyi gunaabadxyiꞌdxyi Herodes loh Jesuhs ya nin tuhbi dxyiꞌdxyi raꞌ chi ayi guñiꞌ Jesuhs.
Ya chin cagacaꞌh raꞌ ba Jesuhs loh cruhzi, chiꞌchi guñiꞌ Jesuhs rahbi Ñiꞌh:
Ya chin guyaꞌloh batehta ba bweꞌltihxi Ñiꞌh loh cruhzi, chiꞌchi batuꞌbi ban laꞌn tuhbi sabna ya bacaꞌtsi ban laꞌn tuhbi baꞌ dxiah hasta nagahdxi chyu bwiinn guigaꞌtsi.
nee laꞌh nu bidiꞌhnn nu lligaaba laꞌh ba ñahca nin ñuldaꞌh laꞌh raꞌ bwiinn Israel laꞌn naa raꞌ bwiinnziitu raꞌ nin rnabwaꞌ raꞌ laꞌh nuꞌh. Yannah guhcala chohnna dxyih guhca cohsa raꞌ riiꞌ,
ya gunaꞌzu Ñiꞌhn gudahw Ñiꞌhn nezloh raꞌ ba,
Ya garaa raꞌ nu, bachicaꞌha raꞌ nu xquelnazaꞌcaduxa Ñiꞌh, nee cun neezaa guelnadziiꞌhi dihtsi lasaaꞌ guelnadziiꞌhi.
―Naꞌh bwaꞌhan biehta Spíritu Saantu nez llaaꞌndxibaaꞌ yihca Jesuhs zigazi tuhbi palohmwiꞌhn ya guzuhdxyii palomwiꞌhn chi yihca ba.
Chiꞌchi rahbi Natanael loh Jesuhs:
Ya ziga laꞌh xlañih paascu raꞌ bwiinn Israel raꞌ zeꞌgadzihn chin riagannastoꞌ raꞌ ba gueꞌla nin gudiiꞌdxi aanjla guelguhchi loh guihdxyi Egiptu, niꞌchin gunaꞌzunehza Jesuhs, zee Ñiꞌh para loh guihdxyi Jerusalehn.
―Per, ¿xa gaca dee raꞌ?
Daada Dxiohs nadziiꞌhi Ñiꞌh laꞌh Lliiꞌn Ñiꞌh nee badiꞌhi za Ñiꞌh guelrnabwaꞌ laꞌh Lliiꞌn Ñiꞌh loh garaatiiꞌ.
―Daada, nnahyi rwaꞌhahn yuꞌbiluꞌh naa luꞌh tuhbi bwiinn nin rñiꞌ xchiꞌdxyi Dxiohs.
chiꞌchi rahbi raꞌ ba loh gunnaꞌh chi:
Chiꞌchi rahbi Jesuhs loh ba:
Rahbi za Jesuhs:
―Riiꞌ laꞌh tuhbi biꞌnxtuhbi zuu laꞌh bi nuꞌa gaꞌyu pahn nin guhcachaꞌyi cun sebada cun chiohpa bwehlda, per ¿calla gaaldaa dee dxiꞌh loh bwiinn ziahan duxa raꞌ ca?
Ya chiꞌchi gunaabadxyiꞌdxyi raꞌ ba loh Ñiꞌh rahbi raꞌ ba:
Chiꞌchi rahbi Jesuhs loh raꞌ ba:
―Ayi dxiaꞌhan luꞌh riiꞌ; gwah para guihdxyi Judea tin riꞌchi neezaa raꞌ xpwiinn raꞌ luꞌh nin caꞌnzanee luꞌh gwaꞌha raꞌ ba garaa raꞌ dziꞌn raꞌ nin ruhnn luꞌh,
Ayi ruhnn tu guelguxchisi pur nin rwaꞌha si tu, sino que chin ruhn tu guelguxchisi, gulguiꞌnnan per ziga naa xnehza.
Nuu raꞌ bwiinn nin guclaaꞌdzi ñanee laꞌh Jesuhs tin ñieꞌw Ñiꞌh, per nin tuhbi za raꞌ ba ayi biaalla ñuhnn ziꞌchi.
―Nin naꞌh za ayi xi duhlda gudziiꞌbaꞌhn yihca luꞌh; pwihsi nnah gwah, ayiru cheezah luꞌh loh duhlda.
―Chin laꞌh tu guiteesa tu laꞌh Lliiꞌn Dxiohs nin naa ndxiꞌhw, chiꞌchi gacabwaꞌ tu naꞌh naan nin naan, nee ayi ruꞌnnahn dziꞌn raꞌ rii pur xcweenta gahcahn; rñiꞌsihn loh tu nin baluuꞌyi Xtaaꞌdahn naꞌh,
―¡Nachidxiaapaa nu rsohn chin rachiñiꞌ nu yiꞌh naa luꞌh tuhbi bwiinn Samaritano nee nuu tuhbi bwiinndxaaba stoꞌ luꞌh!
Nuu raꞌ ba rahbi raꞌ ba: “Laꞌh ban”, ya snuhn raꞌ ba rahbi: “Ayi laꞌh dxiꞌh ban, nicala ziꞌchi rñah ba”, ya laꞌhgahca bwiinn nin ayi biin loh ñiꞌh chi rahbi: “Naꞌhan.”
Ya chiꞌchi gubiaꞌgarii gudihdxyi raꞌ ba bwiinn nin ayi biin loh ñiꞌh chi stuhbi tin rahbi raꞌ ba loh bi:
―¿Ta zee loh xchiꞌdxyi chiꞌh luꞌh nee laꞌh nu naa nu dxieꞌpa?
ya riꞌchi bataꞌwnaa raꞌ bwiinn Israel laꞌh Jesuhs ya rahbi raꞌ ba loh Ñiꞌh:
―Gueldxyihdxyi riiꞌ ayi guunnan gachitiiꞌ Lásaro para tuꞌpazi, sino que nahpa zalluꞌyin tin guluuꞌyin xa naa xquelrnabwaꞌ Dxiohs, nee cun xcweenta za xquelrnabwaꞌ Lliiꞌn Ñiꞌh.
―Pwihsi, naꞌh naꞌnnahn nahpa gabahan raꞌ bwiinn raꞌ nin guhchi dxyih nin gaduhbi guidxyiyuh.
Ya chiꞌchi gudooꞌba raꞌ ba dxiah chi, chiꞌchi bwaꞌha Jesuhs nez llaaꞌndxibaaꞌ chiꞌchi rahbi Ñiꞌh:
―Basaaꞌn si bi, laasii nin cayuhnn bi naa xnehzan cagaꞌbi xgah bi nsehchi riiꞌ naꞌh par laꞌn dxyih nin guigaꞌtsiꞌhn,
Ya garaa raꞌ bwiinn raꞌ nin rii raꞌ riꞌchi rahbi raꞌ ba guziꞌw niꞌchi guñiꞌ, ya snuhn raꞌ ba rahbi:
nee naꞌnnahn dxyiꞌdxyi nin rnabwaꞌ Xtaada Dxiohsaꞌhn zeꞌneen guelnabahan nin ayi ñichilohtiiꞌ para laꞌh raꞌ bwiinn nin riachiistoꞌñin, pwihsi ziga rñiꞌn loh tu, rñiꞌñin loh tu ziga gunabwaꞌ Daada Dxiohs guiñiꞌñin loh tu.
―Guchiin nin rñiꞌn loh tu, tuhbi gahca tu dxiuꞌn ntriehgu naꞌh.
Laꞌh tu ya naann tu neziuh nin zee nez guzaaꞌhahn.
ya loh nin guziaaꞌhahn rusiaꞌhanahn guelrbwihdxyii stoꞌ para laꞌh tu; runiꞌhihn guelrbwihdxyii stoꞌ riiꞌ nin naa xteꞌnnahn laꞌh tu, per nin guniꞌhihn laꞌh tu ayi naan ziga nin rudiꞌhi raꞌ bwiinn guidxyiyuh. Ayi guunn tu ziahan lligaaba, nee ayiza guidxyihbi tu.
Cayahca raꞌ deeꞌ tin soobaa dxyiꞌdxyi nin caa loh xlehyi raꞌ ba: “Bidxyiꞌchinee raꞌ ba naꞌh nicala ayi xi xtuꞌldahn.”
Ziꞌchilla laꞌh tu nnah nuu guelnalaasa stoꞌ tu, per zabiaꞌgarii dxieꞌldaguiaꞌhahn cuun tu ya chiꞌchi ziahxi tu chin gwaꞌha tu naꞌh ya guelriahxi chi ayi chuu nin tuhbi chyu guziaꞌtiiꞌhin loh tu,
Ayi rnaꞌbaꞌhn loh yuꞌbiluꞌh gabweꞌhe luꞌh ba loh guidxyiyuh, sino que gulaloh raꞌ luꞌh laꞌh raꞌ ba loh bwiinndxaaba.
Ya chiꞌchi laꞌh Simohn Pehdru nuꞌa tuhbi spahda, chiꞌchi guleꞌhe ba spahda chi chiꞌchi bachyuuꞌga ba tuhbi lahdu dxiahga derehchu tuhbi bwiinn nin laa Malco, nin naa xmooza tuhbi bixohza nin naa bixohzarooꞌ laꞌn dxyih raꞌ chi,
Ya hohrachi gahca bacaꞌhyahnn dxiidxinguhla.
Ya Barrabahs riiꞌ guhca ba tuhbi gubaꞌn.
―¡Gachi ba! ¡Gachi ba! ¡Bacaꞌh ba loh cruhzi!
―Laꞌn guluhlla.
―Ruꞌnaꞌhn laasii zeenee raꞌ ba bweꞌltihxi Jesuhs, yannah nin ayi rahcabwaꞌn canehza zeenee raꞌ ban.
Ya chiꞌchi rahbi Tomahs:
―Gultaaꞌ tin guxirihn tu.
Ya dxyiꞌdxyi riiꞌ bidiꞌchin loh raꞌ xpwiinn Jesucristu pur xpwiinn Ñiꞌh chi ayi ñahchi ba, per laꞌh Jesuhs ayi guñiꞌ dxiꞌh Ñiꞌh ayi ñahchi ba sino que rahbi Ñiꞌh: “Sidela naꞌh guiclaaꞌdzihn ba nabahan ba chin guibiaꞌgariin stuhbi, ya yiꞌh ¿xiillampoortan luꞌh?”
Neezaa rahbi loh dxihtsi chi:
Zadzihn dxyih nin guixeꞌhlaꞌhn Spíritu Saantuhn tin cweezaa Ñiꞌh laꞌn lastoꞌ garaatiiꞌ bwiinn,
Niꞌchin rñiꞌn loh tu ―rahbi Pehdru―, laꞌhtu nin bacaꞌh laꞌh Jesucristu loh cruhzi, bwiinn Israel raꞌ gulgahcabwaꞌ, laꞌDxiohs bazuh laꞌh Daada Jesucristu tin guinabwaꞌ Ñiꞌh laꞌhnuꞌh neezaa gutaꞌh Ñiꞌh laꞌhnuꞌh loh duhlda.
Xchiohs nuꞌh nin naa Xchiohs guehtu Abrahn, guehtu Isaac, neezaa guehtu Jacobo; laꞌh gahca Dxiohs riiꞌ badiꞌhi guelrnabwaꞌ rooꞌ laꞌh Lliiꞌn Ñiꞌh nin laa Jesuhs. Xlawaaꞌha ñuhnn cweenta tu laꞌh Ñiꞌh, laꞌhlaa mahziru gunaaba tu gudxiinn Pilahtu Ñiꞌh loh Pilahtu. Chin guclaaꞌdzi ba ñuldaꞌh ba laꞌh Ñiꞌh,
yaque laꞌh tu rnabadxyiꞌdxyi tu niꞌchin nnah gachiñiꞌ xnehza nu loh tu nee neezaa loh garaa raꞌ bwiinn guihdxyi Israel, Jesucristu nin bacaꞌh tu loh cruhzi, laꞌDxiohs bacwaꞌhn laꞌh Ñiꞌh loh guelguhchi ya pur lah Ñiꞌh basiaca nu laꞌh bwiinn nin zuu nez loh tu riiꞌ nazaꞌca nnah,
Guhcanee Dxiohs laꞌh raꞌ pooxtla tin baluuꞌyi raꞌ ba guchiipaꞌhcaa babahn Jesucristu loh guelguhchi nee neezaa cayahcanee duxa Dxiohs laꞌh garaa raꞌ xpwiinn Ñiꞌh.
Chin badzihn raꞌ guixaꞌga rwaaꞌ lahtsi dxiꞌba, bwaꞌha raꞌ ba laꞌn lahtsi dxiꞌba chi, ayila chyu nuu laꞌn lahtsi dxiꞌba chi, chiꞌchi gubiaꞌgarii raꞌ ba baganee raꞌ ba dxyiꞌdxyi loh raꞌ guxchiisi nin rnabwaꞌ, rahbi raꞌ ba:
Niꞌchin nnah nahpaa cwii tu loh lasaaꞌ tu gahdzi ndxiꞌhw nin luꞌh naann tu naa bwiinn zaꞌca nin nuu Spíritu Saantu xteenn Dxiohs laꞌn lastoꞌ raꞌ ñiꞌh ya ndxiꞌhw raꞌ chi chiꞌzi xi gahw raꞌ bwiinn.
Ya chin baroopa bweelta riah raꞌ bi, chiꞌchi rahbi Joseh loh raꞌ bi: “Bwiꞌtsihn laꞌh tu”, chiꞌchiyi guhcabwaꞌza Faraohn cuun nin naa raꞌ bwihtsi Joseh.
―Per guehtu xtaada guldooꞌ raꞌ nuꞌh ayi bazoꞌbadxiahga raꞌ ba xchiꞌdxyi guehtu Moisehs ya guclaaꞌdzi raꞌ ba ñibiaꞌgarii raꞌ ba lahdxyi bwiinn Egiptu,
Lwehgu bazuꞌnllihbi Esteban chiꞌchi guñiꞌ ba jweersi rooꞌ:
―Gulguinaaba loh Dxiohs xcweeꞌntahn tin ayi sacaꞌhn ziga guñiꞌ tu.
Chin bareꞌh raꞌ ba loh ñihsa zenee Spíritu Saantu Dxiohs laꞌh Felipe, ya cun ayiru bwaꞌha daada chi laꞌh Felipe, per cun ziaayahxi duxa ba nicala ayi bwaꞌha ru ba laꞌh Felipe.
Naꞌh guluuꞌyiꞌhn laꞌh Saulu cuun trabahjw duxa nin gutiꞌdxiloh ba pur Naꞌh.
Ya seguihdu gahca zeenee Pehdru laꞌh raꞌ daada chi. Chin badzihn Pehdru laꞌn curdohra hasta naꞌ guehtaguhla Dorcas chi, riꞌchi rii raꞌ gunnaꞌh nin cayuꞌn duxa raꞌ, baluuꞌyi raꞌ ba xahba raꞌ ba laꞌh Pehdru nin luꞌh bwiꞌhnn chaꞌyi Dorcas laꞌh raꞌ ba chin nabahan ba.
Tal nin cayuhnn Pehdru lligaaba guiñiꞌ xi niꞌchi nin bwaꞌha ba, badzihn raꞌ ndxiꞌhw nin guxeꞌhla Corneliu rwaaꞌ yihdzi Simohn nin rucuuꞌdzi dxihdxi.
Laꞌhtu naann tu xi guhca cun bwiinn Israel raꞌ, guzaꞌlohon nez guihdxyi Galilea, ya que guyaꞌloh baluuꞌyi Jwahn nahpaa chioobaañihsa raꞌ bwiinn tin cwihsiinn raꞌ ba chin gadzihn Crixtu.
Chiꞌchi bagannaastoꞌn dxyiꞌdxyi nin guñiꞌ Jesucristu, gunnah Ñiꞌh: “Jwahn baroꞌbañihsa cun ñihsa per ya laꞌh tu chioobaañihsa tu cun Spíritu Saantu Dxiohs.”
―Guhta xahba luꞌh tin gudaꞌnaꞌhla naꞌh.
Ya seguihdu baxeꞌhla Spíritu Saantu Dxiohs laꞌh Bernabeh cun Saulu tin guunn raꞌ ba dziꞌn, ya gwah raꞌ ba guihdxyi Seleucia, ya riꞌchi guyuuꞌtii raꞌ ba laꞌn barcu tin zee raꞌ ba loh yuh nin rii galaayi loh ñihsadoꞌ nin laa Chipre.
Bwiinn guihdxyi Jerusalehn raꞌ cun nin rnabwaꞌ za laꞌh raꞌ ba ayi biuꞌnbwaꞌ raꞌ ba laꞌh Jesucristu nin rnabwaꞌ, ayiza guhcabwaꞌ raꞌ ba xchiꞌdxyi Dxiohs nin bacaꞌh guehtu profeta raꞌ dxyiꞌdxyi raꞌ chi nin guñiꞌ raꞌ ba laꞌn guidoꞌ cada dxyih nin ruziꞌlaaꞌdzi raꞌ ba per ayi guhcabwaꞌ raꞌ ban niꞌchin laꞌhlaa laꞌh gahca raꞌ ba bazaꞌloh raꞌ ba ziga bacaꞌh profeta raꞌ pur nin gurih raꞌ ba guhchi Jesucristu.
Ziꞌchizi bidiꞌchii xchiꞌdxyi Jesucristu loh guihdxyi raꞌ chi.
